'Every noise is harmonious now,'

02:01:22.791 --> 02:01:25.041
'Every minute is a aeon now'

02:01:25.458 --> 02:01:26.875
'These words are old'

02:01:27.250 --> 02:01:28.583
'But it feels novel.'

02:01:28.875 --> 02:01:31.041
'And the longing has
crossed its limits'

02:01:31.583 --> 02:01:33.875
